<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Reservation Completion - TravelApp</title>
  {{>partials/head-assets}}
</head>
<body class="page-body">
  {{>partials/header}}

<main class="booking-complete-main-01">
<div class="booking-complete-wrap">
<div class="booking-complete-div-01">
<div class="booking-complete-div-02">
<span class="icon-ms-primary-48-bold">check</span>
</div>
<h2 class="booking-complete-h2-01">예약이 완료되었습니다.</h2>
<p class="booking-complete-p-01">선택하신 숙소 예약이 정상적으로 처리되었습니다.</p>
</div>
<div class="booking-complete-div-03">
<div class="booking-complete-div-04">
<div class="booking-complete-div-05">
<img alt="Hotel Room" class="booking-complete-img-01" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuC-tNVV57D0EwHVcc8AGgHsqFcUf1oHeJUsCxZ-987Qnye2F7JO9sQyk8t_AWfw0W3RDx8bJWwNKOLLAFJe_IIC1x8Pdg3Q6_YzcyaKkC7GitmYoVQPK24H1H4ZGnJYOn_ihHy2Tp-8xS1yfeVoS0dIPgu3UwUeR3w16rvw0eJ-X49iGCKDq0ku2fbWdoYPv_RklQ4NrLhuBb5HSC1KdxB4_6rQkDx3n2Z8l1IsBQTL0F_C2wv7gApGTmObL4V1gUyPs9A2p3zThbw"/>
<div class="booking-complete-div-06"></div>
</div>
<div class="booking-complete-div-07">
<h3 class="booking-complete-h3-01">예약 상세 정보</h3>
<div class="booking-complete-div-08">
<div class="booking-complete-div-09">
<span class="text-muted-sm-medium">예약 번호</span>
<span class="booking-complete-span-01">KR-20231025-001</span>
</div>
<div class="booking-complete-div-09">
<span class="text-muted-sm-medium">숙소 이름</span>
<span class="booking-complete-span-02">서울 롯데 호텔</span>
</div>
<div class="booking-complete-div-09">
<span class="text-muted-sm-medium">지역</span>
<div class="booking-complete-div-10">
<span class="icon-ms-sm-muted">location_on</span>
<span class="booking-complete-span-03">서울, 대한민국</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class="booking-complete-div-09">
<span class="text-muted-sm-medium">인원 수</span>
<span class="booking-complete-span-02">성인 2명</span>
</div>
<div class="booking-complete-div-11">
<span class="text-muted-sm-medium">체크인 / 체크아웃</span>
<div class="booking-complete-div-12">
<span class="icon-ms-primary">calendar_today</span>
<span class="booking-complete-span-04">2023.11.10 (금) - 2023.11.12 (일)</span>
<span class="booking-complete-span-05">2박</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class="booking-complete-div-13">
<div class="row-between-end">
<span class="booking-complete-span-06">총 결제 금액</span>
<span class="booking-complete-span-07">₩450,000</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="booking-complete-div-14">
<span class="icon-ms-sm-green-500">verified_user</span>
<span class="booking-complete-span-08">결제가 안전하게 완료되었습니다.</span>
</div>
</div>
<p class="booking-complete-p-02">
<span class="mr-2-fixed">💡</span>예약 정보는 자동으로 여행 계획과 캘린더에 등록되었습니다.
        </p>
<div class="booking-complete-div-15">
<button class="booking-complete-button-01">
<span class="icon-ms-20">map</span>
                여행 계획 보기
            </button>
<button class="booking-complete-button-02">
<span class="icon-ms-20">calendar_month</span>
                캘린더 확인하기
            </button>
</div>
<div class="mt-6">
<a class="fx-group-link-muted" href="#">
<span class="icon-ms-18-hover-left">arrow_back</span>
                탐색으로 돌아가기
            </a>
</div>
</div>
</main>

  {{>partials/chatbot}}
  {{>partials/footer}}
  {{>partials/scripts}}
</body>
</html>
